            "body": "Thanks [~Weihao Zheng] for filling this ticket!\r\n\r\nI think it's very useful for cluster management, and it's reasonable to use the non-specified-queue configuration as some cluster-level configurations already did (e.g. yarn.scheduler.capacity.maximum-applications / yarn.scheduler.capacity.maximum-am-resource-percent / yarn.scheduler.capacity.max-parallel-apps).\r\n\r\nFor the PR, I think it's better to add a simple UT in\u00a0TestApplicationLimit and make sure\u00a0the related document is updated.",
